Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on cases with Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE before re-submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in cases where re-submission occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Request Payment in successful cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases involving both rejections
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER in cases that are re-submitted and then approved by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for cases that are re-submitted after rejection
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time it takes for a Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be followed by any approval activity
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'", 'end': "activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' or activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' or activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' or activity == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'", 'aggregation': 'average'}

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after a Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs
